OL,3,CPolice chiefs say Labour's anti-crime
OL,4,Cpromises will not happen without more
OL,5,Ccash
OL,7,FSix of Britain's top cops have
OL,8,Fdemanded a "substantial investment" in
OL,9,Fpolicing, as ITV News Political
OL,10,FCorrespondent Harry Horton reports
OL,12,FPolice chiefs are warning the
OL,13,Fgovernment will not hit its anti-crime
OL,14,Ftargets without "substantial
OL,15,Finvestment" in policing in next
OL,16,Fmonth's spending review.
