OL,3,CPolice chiefs say Labour's anti-crime
OL,4,Cpromises will not happen without more
OL,5,Ccash
OL,7,FIn a letter published in The Times,
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,9,FMark Rowley, NPCC chairman Constable
OL,10,FGavin Stephens, and the chiefs of
OL,11,FMerseyside, West Midlands, Greater
OL,12,FManchester and West Yorkshire police ,
OL,13,Fwarned of a return to the
OL,14,F"retrenchment we saw under austerity"
OL,15,Fwithout increased funding for police
OL,16,Fforces.
OL,18,FSir Keir Starmer has promised to halve
OL,19,Fboth knife crime and violence against
OL,20,Fwomen and girls, and to recruit 13,000
OL,21,Fmore police officers.
