OL,7,FThe letter warned of "increasing
OL,8,Fpublic demand, growing social
OL,9,Fvolatility - such as last summer's
OL,10,Fdisorder ` and new serious and
OL,11,Forganised crime threats emboldened by
OL,12,Fthe online world", along with
OL,13,Fincreased "global insecurity".
OL,15,FThe move is a bid to secure more
OL,16,Ffunding for the Home Office in the
OL,17,FChancellor's spending review in June,
OL,18,Fwhich will set budgets for government
OL,19,Fdepartments until 2029.
