OL,7,FThe Times reports the Home Office will
OL,8,Fhave to make cuts, after what the
OL,9,Fpolice chiefs call a "decade of
OL,10,Funderinvestment in policing".
OL,12,FThe senior police officers say that
OL,13,Fafter global instability led to an
OL,14,Fincrease in defence spending, the same
OL,15,Freasoning should also be applied to
OL,16,Fpolicing to tackle '"the linked
OL,17,Fthreats and growing demands".
