OL,7,FCraig Guildford, Chief Constable of
OL,8,FWest Midlands Police, told ITV News he
OL,9,Fis "concerned about returning to an
OL,10,Fera of austerity, because we still
OL,11,Fbare some of those scars."
OL,13,F"Society is changing, the nature of
OL,14,Fcrime is changing, and we have to keep
OL,15,Fup with that", Guildford said.
