OL,7,FThat contradicts the view of former
OL,8,Fjustice secretary and author of the
OL,9,Fsentencing review David Gauke, along
OL,10,Fwith other prison reform experts, who
OL,11,Fsay community sentences are proven to
OL,12,Fcut reoffending.
OL,14,FJustice Secretary, Shabana Mahmood,
OL,15,Fhas also agreed to allow some
OL,16,Fcriminals, including violent and
OL,17,Fsexual offenders, to be released early
OL,18,Ffor good behaviour.
