OL,7,FIn a separate plea, other senior crime
OL,8,Fbodies have also called on the
OL,9,Fgovernment for more funding amid
OL,10,Fpressures from the plans to release
OL,11,Fprisoners early.
OL,13,FThe heads of the Metropolitan Police,
OL,14,FMI5 and the National Crime Agency were
OL,15,Famong those who warned that plans to
OL,16,Frelease prisoners early could be "of
OL,17,Fnet detriment to public safety" in a
OL,18,Fletter to the Ministry of Justice.
